<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 0; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); background-color: white; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; }
        .header p { margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        .greeting { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .credentials-box { background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 25px 0; font-family: 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace; }
        .credential-row { margin: 12px 0; }
        .credential-label { font-weight: 600; color: #555; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .credential-value { font-size: 14px; color: #000; margin-top: 4px; word-break: break-all; }
        .button-container { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
        .button:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
        .info-box { background-color: #e7f3ff; border-left: 4px solid #2196F3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 13px; }
        .info-box strong { color: #1976D2; }
        .security-note { background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 13px; }
        .security-note strong { color: #ff6b00; }
        .role-badge { display: inline-block; background-color: #667eea; color: white; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 8px; }
        .footer { background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; font-size: 12px; color: #777; }
        .footer p { margin: 5px 0; }
        .divider { height: 1px; background-color: #e0e0e0; margin: 20px 0; }
        ul { margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; }
        li { margin: 8px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to CDR Billing System</h1>
            <p>Your account has been created successfully</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                <p>Dear <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</p>
                <p>Welcome! Your account has been successfully created in the CDR Billing System. You can now access the platform using the credentials provided below.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="credentials-box">
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <div class="credential-label">Email Address</div>
                    <div class="credential-value"><%= email %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <div class="credential-label">Temporary Password</div>
                    <div class="credential-value"><%= password %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="credential-row">
                    <div class="credential-label">Your Role</div>
                    <div><span class="role-badge"><%= role.replace(/-/g, ' ').toUpperCase() %></span></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="<%= portalUrl %>" class="button">Login to Portal</a>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Next Steps:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use the credentials above to log in to the portal</li>
                    <li>After logging in, you can update your password for security</li>
                    <li>Explore your dashboard and available features based on your role</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="security-note">
                <strong>⚠️ Security Important:</strong>
                Please change your password immediately after your first login. Keep your credentials confidential and never share them with anyone.
            </div>

            <div>
                <p><strong>Account Details:</strong></p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %><br>
                    <strong>Role:</strong> <%= role.replace(/-/g, ' ').charAt(0).toUpperCase() + role.replace(/-/g, ' ').slice(1) %><br>
                    <% if (phone) { %><strong>Phone:</strong> <%= phone %><br><% } %>
                </p>
            </div>
           

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>CDR Billing System Team</strong></p>
            <% if (logoSrc) { %>
            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="text-align: left;">
                        <img src="<%= logoSrc %>" alt="Cyvora" style="max-width: 120px; width: 120px; height: auto; display: block;" />
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> CDR Billing System. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
